                        Go West on US Airways
       Hurry! Purchase Tickets by Wednesday, February 6, 2002
       ------------------------------------------------------

Go West on US Airways with sale fares starting at $298 roundtrip, for travel between most cities in the eastern U.S. and Las Vegas, San Diego, San Francisco or Seattle.

To take advantage of these great sale fares, book online at http://www.usairways.com/promotions/specials/east_west_sale.htm no later than February 6, 2002.

Sale Details:
-------------
- Tickets must be purchased online at usairways.com at least 7 days before departure
  and no later than February 6, 2002
- All travel must be completed by April 30, 2002
- Travel Monday-Thursday for lowest sale fares
- See Sale Fare Requirements below for complete details


Earn More Miles When You Book Online
------------------------------------
Receive 1000 bonus Dividend Miles each time you purchase a roundtrip ticket online and fly on US Airways now through May 31, 2002. Visit http://www.usairways.com/dividendmiles/offers/usairways.htm#booking prior to departure for complete details.


This is just a sample of the sale fares offered.  Fares are good for travel in either direction.  For reservations and fares from your city go to http://www.usairways.com/promotions/specials/east_west_sale.htm


